## Synopsis

This is a term project for CSE324 course (0.75 credit hour(s)) at Dept of CSE, BUET. We, in a group of two members, tried to implement an e-commerce site.

## Code Example

In this demo e-commerce site we had product buying and selling system, blog for customer review. We just wanted to implement a fancy site for our academic course work.

## Motivation

Academic purpose.

## Installation

clone this project.
Setup virtualenv and install all dependencies as mentioned in requirements.txt file.

